Description:
You arrive at the entrance of the castle. Strangely, there's no sign of guards or security.

Only scattered pieces of armor lie ahead, blocking the path. A faint fog clings to them, shifting ever so slightly in the breeze.

You'll need to clear the way to proceed.
DescriptionAction: How do you want to handle this?
